  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to compare the efficacy of gastric balloon in weight reduction among
      two different categories of morbidly obese people.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To study to effect of gastric balloon in weight reduction among those above 35 BMI and those
      above 45 BMI.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
